Features of Bowling Alley
1. Two Players will be added to Bowling game. Each player takes chances alternatively. Each player will have 2 throws on each chance.
2. No of Pins fallen is their score.
3. If they strike(all fallen) on first throw, they are given another fresh formation(only once) which in turn will have 2 throws. Hence in this case there will be three throws for a chance.
4. Each player will be provided 10 chances in each game. Score will be cumulative of all chances.
5. Player with highest score wins